{"tid":1762112,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"杜浩成參加母校50周年校慶！","createTime":"2019-11-29T10:57:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T16:34:36.000Z","uid":233156,"like":142,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"2f056e1a37b1cdb1640d38219ab3245f56299eda","tid":1762112,"uid":233156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T10:57:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/862bJ6X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F862bJ6X.png&h=b5ea9596&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係呢條仆街</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">7/12 同 8/12</span></span><br />\n就係佢母校<br />\n陳瑞祺(喇沙)書院<br />\n嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">50周年</span>校慶<br />\n佢呢啲咁特別嘅人一定會參加<br />\n歡迎大家可以同佢一齊去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />學校開放日參觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果到時搞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嚟唔到就唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗起見到林夕同佢對槍都覺得好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wmRG6mQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwmRG6mQ.jpg&h=edbdb856&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gfdyc1R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGfdyc1R.jpg&h=657e4832&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"723d0acc2cc8ca673b40794f4bb0172bac104a23","tid":1762112,"uid":233156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T10:58:23.000Z","msg":"721 <br />\n831<br />\n101"},{"pid":"99cecda920ed3571246048fd535760164b978b01","tid":1762112,"uid":108337,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T10:58:56.000Z","msg":"獅鳥"},{"pid":"432909136d5dfd1d6e78abb209b41d0d5105f36e","tid":1762112,"uid":8014,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"99cecda920ed3571246048fd535760164b978b01","tid":1762112,"uid":108337,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T10:58:56.000Z","msg":"獅鳥"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T11:00:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.calbee.com.hk/img/imagecache/280x333_BBQ_l.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.calbee.com.hk%2Fimg%2Fimagecache%2F280x333_BBQ_l.png&h=3f6169d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a91342c429dca94baba4dbe2ce0260f4d7a80ebe","tid":1762112,"uid":247032,"like":66,"dislike":1,"score":65,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T11:03:52.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母 仆佢個街<br />\n<br />\n1. 一名男子去年十二月參與「愛護香港力量」撐政府遊行期間，在眾目睽睽之下襲擊電視台攝影師，杜浩成則僅判案中被告罰款一千五百元及賠償一千元。<br />\n<br />\n2. 杜浩成將13-15歲的學童判入屯門兒童及青少年院，被兒童權利委員會質疑決定會影響他們接受教育的機會及受父母照顧的權利。<br />\n<br />\n3. 休班警Uniqlo偷竊案：杜浩成法官稱兩次於Uniqlo盜竊的被告為出色的警員，判自簽1,000元，守行為12個月。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"110214f04007c52166793838dea3301d5d073714","tid":1762112,"uid":259901,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"a91342c429dca94baba4dbe2ce0260f4d7a80ebe","tid":1762112,"uid":247032,"like":66,"dislike":1,"score":65,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T11:03:52.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母 仆佢個街<br />\n<br />\n1. 一名男子去年十二月參與「愛護香港力量」撐政府遊行期間，在眾目睽睽之下襲擊電視台攝影師，杜浩成則僅判案中被告罰款一千五百元及賠償一千元。<br />\n<br />\n2. 杜浩成將13-15歲的學童判入屯門兒童及青少年院，被兒童權利委員會質疑決定會影響他們接受教育的機會及受父母照顧的權利。<br />\n<br />\n3. 休班警Uniqlo偷竊案：杜浩成法官稱兩次於Uniqlo盜竊的被告為出色的警員，判自簽1,000元，守行為12個月。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T11:04:39.000Z","msg":"唔好請佢食叔一燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba774e9bbe94ac473b2320566075d